title: Raidpictures.rar
description:
Raid pictures from February 10th 2008 Anonymous vs Church of Scientology.

This archive contains raid pictures from CoS locations all around the world.
It does not include all pictures from all locations because the file would be too big.

Instead it contains the best shots i have handpicked from CoS raids in all locations i could find. Sums up to about 650 pics.

Enjoy.

~Anondelivers
